parameters: There's a DVD on the ground!
Memimi: Brachiocondor! Someone left their DVD behind...

Brachiocondor: Tch... It's his, isn't it. Always leaving
stuff behind. Hmm, is this a shark movie...?

Bunny-chan: That looks interesting! Hey, hey, let's watch it
together?

Memimi: Hmm, secretly developed during the war... I see, a
Franken-shark, is it? This is exciting, let's watch it!
Brachiocondor: That movie is... well, never mind...

Memimi: Aha, the empire's biological weapon... I see, so
this affected the shark... It must be incredibly strong!!
Memimi: ...I'm going to get some fresh air outside...

Memimi: ...That's right, in wrestling there is a move called
the Frankensteiner... I should ask the great boss to teach
me...
There's a DVD on the ground!
Memimi: Brachiocondor! Someone left their DVD behind...

Brachiocondor: Tch... It's his, isn't it. Always leaving
stuff behind. Hmm, is this a shark movie...?

Bunny-chan: That looks fun! Hey, hey, let's all watch it
together?

Memimi: Hmm, secretly developed during the war... I see, a
Franken-shark, is it? This is getting exciting, let's watch
it!
Brachiocondor: That movie is... well, never mind...

Memimi: Aha, the empire's biological weapon... I see, so
this affected the shark... It must be incredibly strong!!
Memimi: ...I'm going to get some fresh air outside...

Memimi: ...That's right, in pro wrestling there's a move
called the Frankensteiner... I should ask the great boss to
teach me...

Brachiocondor: Gahaha, Anomalocaris was clearly a formidable
opponent. You did well to win!! Shark Broccoli was also
happily drinking away.

Memimi: If the great boss is pleased, then my efforts were
worth it. But I don't fight just for the boss. It's because
I'm prepared to dedicate myself for the true peace of the
city that I can unleash this power...

Brachiocondor: More than unifying the city... improving the
public order and economy of Dorobachi City is also our
earnest wish. Especially for Shark Broccoli, he probably
feels a sense of guilt about that incident...

Brachiocondor: Oops... I can't say any more from my mouth...
Eventually, you'll hear it from Shark Broccoli himself...

Memimi: In the past, between Shark Broccoli the great boss
and Dorobachi City, what happened...

Brachiocondor: Cerberus Octopus, huh... He uses a powerful
martial art based on boxing. I never clashed with him during
my active days, but if we had fought, it wouldn't have been
easy.

Memimi: There's no doubt he's one of the strongest monsters
in the city, but there are ways to defeat him... Compared to
you or Anomalocaris, his defense and physique are inferior.
The lack of weight is a significant disadvantage in a
fight...

Brachiocondor: You're the one I think has the least weight
among all the monsters in the city though...

Brachiocondor: What's with that bizarre suit... It's a total
mess... Doesn't Cerberus Octopus have any morals...?

Memimi: Damn it... So, so frustrating... To be exposed like
this to so many people... And so many people I know saw
me... Ahh...

Bunny-chan: Poor Memimi-chan... Please don't look too
much...

Brachiocondor: Gahaha... No need to worry, I'm devoted to my
wife!! I'm not so weak-willed as to lust after women under
thirty!!

Brachiocondor: A store that sells food shouldn't be doing
those dirty campaigns where you lick and taste such filthy
things. It's not commendable at all. It'll be too late once
something happens!

Memimi: Personally, I think something has already happened!!
It's dirty, it stinks!! And I'm full of weird fluids... ugh,
I feel sick...

Bunny-chan: She cried... That was just too much... I used to
shop a lot at Jagged Mart, but now it's become hard to even
get close.

Brachiocondor: Shark Broccoli must be feeling frustrated. In
truth, he himself still wants to fight. He's still in his
20s, after all...

Bunny-chan: He was in his 20s, huh~. By the way, why did
Shark Broccoli-san retire? He was already gone when I joined
the management team...

Brachiocondor: His monster suit is falling apart due to wear
and tear... Probably, it wouldn't last another match. It's
the price he's paid for fighting all these years...

Memimi: Also, the monster suit of the great boss is made of
a slightly different material than the others, and it can't
be washed. When you grapple with him, there's a...
unbearable smell, and there have been complaints from his
opponents...
Bunny-chan: In that case, retirement was inevitable...

Brachiocondor: The underground organizations in Doritoku
City often make money through illegal activities. Like
acting as bodyguards, or running shops in secret from the
authorities...

Brachiocondor: However, things like prostitution, drowning
in soaplands, or shooting adult videos are rarely their
gig... In fact, I've never seen it before! There are very
few female members, and monsters generally aren't popular
with the ladies...

Memimi: That's for the best... The fewer unfortunate girls
there are, the better... I wish I were the only one to go
through this... *sob*... *sniffle*...

Brachiocondor: Well, don't worry about it... Want some
juice...?

Brachiocondor: Today's the day we'll win for sure!! Even
Shark Broccoli and the guys from the organization are
worried... They were all gathered here yesterday, grumbling
about it.

Memimi: Thank you, Brachiocondor... I can't let this
situation drag on any longer either. Let's settle it
tonight...

Brachiocondor: That's the spirit!! If we lose again, they're
planning to negotiate selling the right to cross-dress sex
with a good-looking member as a substitute, so you can be
released.
Memimi: We must win at all costs...

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan, great job! The match with
Anomalocaris Mosman-san was so exciting. You looked so cool!

Memimi: You did a great job as the referee too, Bunny-chan.
That was the best match I've ever had... It was truly a
close call.

Bunny-chan: The odds were all over the place until the end.
Of course, I bet on you, Memimi-chan, so I made a nice
little profit♪ I'll treat you today!
Memimi: You were betting, huh... That's pretty shrewd...

Bunny-chan: Do your best in today's match too, Memimi-chan♪
I'm neutral, but I'm rooting for you to win. I also like
Cerberus Octopus-san's matches because they're flashy and he
has a lot of moves.

Memimi: Hehe, it's going to be another great match tonight,
so look forward to it! Knowing that you're watching, Bunny-
chan, gives me peace of mind to fight.

Bunny-chan: Eek... You walked here from the hideout dressed
like that? That's way too reckless—just refuse it...

Memimi: Of course, even within the hierarchy of a dark
organization, orders that go too far are despised as sexual
harassment or power harassment... Even if not, for example,
if I were to cry and beg for forgiveness, surely my
treatment would improve greatly.

Memimi: But still...! Could the monstrous Shark Duke...
Could a subordinate of the great Shark Broccoli-sama ever
expose such disgrace!? Being seen naked is nothing compared
to... ugh... ughhh...!!

Bunny-chan: Ehh, licking a guy's... that? And everyone who
comes to the convenience store... Huh, what's it like? The
taste and all...

Memimi: Bunny-chan seems really curious... Have you been
licking your boyfriend's or something? You must have more
experience with men than I do...

Bunny-chan: I go to an all-girls school, and the staff at
Monster Fight are all old men, so I don't have anyone like
that. I really want a boyfriend though...

Memimi: Well... it would be a lie to say I don't want one...
but it would have to be a man who's my equal...

Bunny-chan: Hijacking the TV show really wore me out...
There's so much groundwork to do, and then there's using the
camera and getting the timing right... I wish we could stop
doing that kind of thing...

Memimi: I totally wish we could stop... I seriously cried
all night... It must have been tough for you too, Bunny-
chan...

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan, you're too hard on yourself, you
should learn to give up a little more...

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan, it's showing, it's showing...!
Cover it up— even if we're both girls, it's embarrassing...

Memimi: It's too late... there's no way to hide it... Even
if I use my hands, I can't cover everything, and it just
ends up looking more lewd... I have no choice but to live
with my lower half exposed... *sniffle*...

Bunny-chan: I think you should apologize to Cerberus
Octopus-sama and ask him to make you a proper monster
suit...

Bunny-chan: Memimi-chan, you absolutely have to win today! I
know I shouldn't really take sides because of my position...
but it's just too painful to watch any more of this...

Memimi: Thank you for worrying about me, Bunny-chan... I'm
seriously at my limit too... I'll win no matter what...

Bunny-chan: If you lose again, I think it might be better to
retire... If it goes on like this, even if you quit being a
monster, you won't be able to live a normal life... Escaping
while you can is also a form of courage, you know~.

Bunny-chan: ...No, maybe it's already... hopeless... or
maybe, just barely...?

Memimi: Stop saying that...! I know my situation better than
anyone else...!

Anomalocaris: Grr... A failed coup d'état... I won't give
up, one day I'll defeat you and take over Doriet City...

Memimi: I'll think of the most ruthless conditions possible,
so feel free to challenge me anytime... You did well,
indeed...

Brachiocondor: Public defecation is a no-go, man. It's
actually better that you passed out before it happened! No
matter how cool and strong a monster you are, nobody's gonna
follow someone who strips naked and poops in front of the
station!

Bunny-chan: Aside from the naked pooping, Anomalocaris-san's
true face was so cool~♪ Show us your face~?

Anomalocaris: Hey... stop that! Seriously! Cool, huh? Could
it be that she actually likes me...? Thump thump...

Memimi: Having a handsome face is fine, but with a monster's
body, you just look like an incredible freak...
